list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: Put Greedy algorithm into project / added a method (reajust) to mapping so that for any ordering of an alphabet of the same size of the roman alphabet or smaller, the output will be displayable using ASCII characters / implemented method to write results to a text file.

task.summary: Changed CsvFileWriter class: Created a new directory "results" inside the project and changed the hard coded field for the result file path (which would only work in one machine with the specified path) to the working directory of the project using System.getProperty("users.dir") plus the directory name ("results").

Changed generateRandomPopulation() method in the Population class because the first order of the alphabet added to the population was the order in which the alphabet was given. It was changed so that the list is shuffle before the first time that is used.
